    "body": "When the gas is set to **450000** the transaction failed with the error: ``` AssertionError: Returned error: Error: Transaction reverted and Hardhat couldn't infer the reason. Please report this to help us improve Hardhat.```\r\n```\r\neth_sendTransaction\r\n  Contract call:       <UnrecognizedContract>\r\n  Transaction:         0xfaaf8b1ea04856e197a4f31a976b115ccbe71ca1bd5648d753d777c6eed33921\r\n  From:                0x9965507d1a55bcc2695c58ba16fb37d819b0a4dc\r\n  To:                  0x9e02f3a8567587d27d7eb1d087408d062b4c6a1c\r\n  Value:               0 ETH\r\n  Gas used:            443477 of 450000\r\n  Block #171:          0x022346ae23fb46a56791bf3010defbfb505dc68f2c93ce83e4d282109fa398ef\r\n\r\n  Error: Transaction reverted and Hardhat couldn't infer the reason. Please report this to help us improve Hardhat.\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd when the gas is set to **550000** the transaction got executed without error. \r\n```\r\neth_sendTransaction\r\n  Contract call:       <UnrecognizedContract>\r\n  Transaction:         0x9f12eb38792cb7218ccb49121eda3140a0a3fd6884d8ba15987f707cee9c39dc\r\n  From:                0x9965507d1a55bcc2695c58ba16fb37d819b0a4dc\r\n  To:                  0xc641b89a8d3d81151c6cd2f05fa593c95d2c1ffc\r\n  Value:               0 ETH\r\n  Gas used:            466401 of 550000\r\n  Block #228:          0x2356eb4346fb1531f4fe093faeb596ddad07ee7e9a01e7ebf18a0f1de1fd50a1\r\n```\r\n\r\nHardhat should throw low gas fees error when gas is set lower than used gas, but the error thrown was  ```AssertionError: Returned error: Error: Transaction reverted and Hardhat couldn't infer the reason. Please report this to help us improve Hardhat.``` which made me clueless why the transaction was being rejected.",
